OL,5,G1550 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt the Newholme Hotel in
OL,7,     FBlackpool, Nigel and Damian offer
OL,8,     Fbudget prices with high-end
OL,9,     Ftouches. But a surprise in the loo
OL,10,     Fand a slimy serving at breakfast
OL,11,     Fcause serious concerns.
OL,12,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FLiz and Tracey host at
OL,14,     FPortsonachan Hotel in Argyll and
OL,15,     FBute. Some dirty discoveries
OL,16,     Fdampen the guests' initial
OL,17,     Fdelight, and a guided tour of
OL,18,     FInveraray Castle serves up some
OL,19,     Fspooky tales.
