OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe final visit is to Lamlash Bay
OL,7,     FHotel on the Isle of Arran. As
OL,8,     Fformer cabin crew, host Meg hopes
OL,9,     Fher customer service will fly her
OL,10,     Fto victory. But a follicle failure
OL,11,     Ftaints her feedback.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FOn the final day of the
OL,14,     Fcompetition, the B&Bers rifle
OL,15,     Fthrough their feedback, from a
OL,16,     Flavatory let-down to fiddled
OL,17,     FFrench toast, before the payments
OL,18,     Fare revealed and the winner is
OL,19,     Fannounced.
