OL,5,G1750 Ugly House to Lovely House with...
OL,6,     F...George Clarke: There are ugly
OL,7,     Fhouses, and then there's Nick and
OL,8,     FSonia's house. Can architects
OL,9,     Ftransform their foul flat into a
OL,10,     Freal home? And what will the
OL,11,     Fneighbours think?
OL,12,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,13,     FWe catch up with Georgie and Louis
OL,14,     Fin London. Are they still in the
OL,15,     Fflat Kirstie secured for them? And
OL,16,     Fhave Lauren and Noel injected
OL,17,     Fcharacter into their
OL,18,     FNorthumberland new build?
