OL,12,G2305 999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     FOn the night shift in Birmingham,
OL,14,     Fparamedics are called to a man
OL,15,     Fwho's had a seizure. But they're
OL,16,     Fwarned that the patient has a
OL,17,     Fhistory of being abusive towards
OL,18,     Fambulance crews.
